---
// Support component
---

<section id="support" class="support-section">
	<div class="support-container">
		<h2 class="support-title">支持我們</h2>
		
		<div class="support-content">
			<p class="support-paragraph">
				SITCON 秉持著不向與會者收費的原則，十年以來致力於推廣學生資訊教育，創造學生交流、教學互長的機會。
			</p>
			
			<p class="support-paragraph">
				如果您也認同 SITCON 的理念，歡迎以行動支持 SITCON 的運作，點擊下方「個人贊助方案」，您的支持將會成為我們的動力，讓更多學生能在舞台上展現自我、讓資訊教育遍及臺灣的每個角落！
			</p>
			
			<p class="support-paragraph">
				若您有興趣成為我們的贊助夥伴，歡迎點擊下方「索取贊助徵求書」，了解詳細合作方案，或是利用 contact@sitcon.org 聯絡我們，我們將有專人與您商討更多的合作方式！
			</p>
		</div>
		
        <div class="support-button-container">
            <button onclick="window.open('https://sitcon.org/2026/cfs/', '_blank')" class="support-button">前往贊助徵求網頁 ↗</button>
        </div>
		
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.support-section {
        position: relative;
        margin: 0 auto;
		background-color: #ffffff;
		padding: 4rem 10rem;
		min-height: 70vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.support-container {
		width: 100%;
		padding: 0 40px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.support-title {
		font-size: 4rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		color: #000000;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		line-height: 1.2;
        letter-spacing: 0.35rem;
	}

	.support-content {
		margin-bottom: 3rem;
	}

	.support-paragraph {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.15rem;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: #000000;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	}

	.support-paragraph:last-of-type {
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.support-button-container {
		margin-top: 2rem;
		display: flex;
		justify-content: end;
	}

	.support-button {
		background-color: #4285F4;
		color: #ffffff;
		border: none;
		padding: 16px 32px;
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		cursor: pointer;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.3);
		display: inline-flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 8px;
	}

	.support-button:hover {
		background-color: #3367D6;
		box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.4);
	}

	.support-button:active {
		transform: translateY(0);
		box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(66, 133, 244, 0.3);
	}

	/* Responsive design */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.support-section {
			padding: 2rem 0;
		}

		.support-title {
			font-size: 3rem;
		}

		.support-paragraph {
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}

		.support-button {
			padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
			font-size: 1.25rem;
		}
	}
</style>
